  <header><h2>Radio Show on RaBe</h2></header>
  <p>
    20 something years ago, some beautiful creatures founded Radio Bern RaBe.
    Today it is the only radio station around who actually lives true freedom, true diversity (as in people and in music) and true culture.
    I seriously could not be happier to be part of the RaBe family and to present a show full of guitars and love every Tuesday Morning from 8-11h
    together with my co-host Nik.
  </p>
  <p>
